sitecopy (1.2.9) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Removed hardcoded 'localhost' for $REMOTE_DBHOST. This ensures that a
    custom database host are applied to remote db.cnf
  * Added exit statement to the end of script to properly run trap
    sequence (exit codes have always been redundant because of trap and
    should be removed)

